只取少量內容，放link鼓勵點擊（尢其文宣大台該帶頭做）。<br />\n<br />\n再重覆，目標為上，才可以拯救連登垂死的熱門。<br />\n<br />\n比方說，<br />\n1. 如果兩日後有遊行，專注推行動Post；<br />\n2. 同一議題，集中處理，不要分散；<br />\n3. 有人留言「拉」，網友不需再留言；<br />\n4. 戒除政治J女性癖，不要再討論區議員身材；<br />\n5. 未能Fact Check的事情，忍痛讓佢沉。<br />\n6. 減少用極端字眼，例如「就嚟輸」；<br />\n7. 至為重要：不 要 再 推 假 標 題<br />\n<br />\n每個手足都有責任打好呢場資訊戰，改變習慣，重奪輿論主導權，大家一定做得到。<br />\n<br />\nYoutube戰線：黃色資訊片一律Coment+Like+Share&amp;Subscribe（CLS)（share做唔到的話重要片先share)<br />\n<br />\n香港人，改變。<br />\n<br />\nP.S.如果覺得有意思，煩請分享，謝謝你。<br />\n-------------------------------------------<br />\nIG：Terry_yeung_blog<br />\nIG連結：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2IMS6HI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2IMS6HI&d=1mfmSgVVN%2FWy7xf%2FaESqF4RM%2FwdnRWUJBfohchWxIRY%3D&h=6d1a9364\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2IMS6HI</a>"},{"pid":"4a5517f23540c7f406f54085dbaf915dee3cdc63","tid":1889693,"uid":160176,"like":52,"dislike":0,"score":52,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T18:01:57.000Z","msg":"其實有無藉口都好<br />\n狗都會要求最好既醫療＋裝備<br />\n然後林奠和支共都會全數提供<br />\n除非醫護罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0bd8ec1dce5ec90331aa5f36fa4210c2548b641","tid":1889693,"uid":1886,"like":72,"dislike":0,"score":72,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T18:02:00.000Z","msg":"都係 J 一晚啫<br />\n可唔可以唔好咁嚴厲<br />\n畀大家 relax 一陣得唔得"},{"pid":"af2b95c69b846a3527525199887e0b6cc1b04d22","tid":1889693,"uid":232845,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T18:02:04.000Z","msg":"打擊對家士氣，慶祝下無妨"},{"pid":"901a3ff5f0804db84ae1f1615a716f2be791729a","tid":1889693,"uid":199670,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"91baaba6fb4ead530aad036da1a7a562e5141ef5","tid":1889693,"uid":242605,"like":16,"dislike":3,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T18:00:51.000Z","msg":"麻煩各位手足幫手推上熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n極速訂閱 黃色頻道<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RDORH0t.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=htt