RWUJBfohchWxIRY%3D&h=6d1a9364\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2IMS6HI</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T18:27:24.000Z","msg":"佢自己咪又係非正統媒體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自相矛盾叫人share<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T18:32:26.000Z","msg":"你個腦去左邊？  家陣話非正統媒體就唔可能生存？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  人地段野自己idea自己諗存喎  而家講緊太多非正統媒體抄新聞唔比link唔比credit喎<br />\n獨立思考呢沖出黎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T18:36:39.000Z","msg":"講下笑都起晒鋼做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我無話唔認同佢講嘅嘢，我夠知背後原因唔一樣<br />\n純粹覺得非正統媒體，用非正統媒介，叫人唔好睇非正統媒體有啲諷刺啫<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d06bebf6e283ddb9a923e6e04b4539846d2e9b40","tid":1889693,"uid":281328,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T18:36:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>未</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>我好撚柒開心高興</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>黑警死完呀爸死呀媽</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"6adf0a5af76ab0e8bc08a5bdcb99b9f6ba3364f1","tid":1889693,"uid":292130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T18:37:06.000Z","msg":"除咗打飛機，諗唔到有咩可以做。"},{"pid":"9c892850922aa651201d888d6dd41d9550804f24","tid":1889693,"uid":33959,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"236f5fe07f3aa13bdbdfcdf4890cc9807e784d41","tid":1889693,"uid":59976,"like":3,"dislike":19,"score":-16,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T18:02:39.000Z","msg":"成班又俾人帶風向走去慶祝，聽日721行動post已經沉哂底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T18:38:43.000Z","msg":"屌真係要記得嘅你唔撚開po都會記